{"tid":1157132,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"唔通依個就係傳說中嘅Perfect body？","createTime":"2019-05-16T05:12:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T15:45:59.000Z","uid":231132,"like":12,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f32685696bc4945096d1ebe15835a0635dd38b61","tid":1157132,"uid":231132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T05:12:56.000Z","msg":"韓國女星李聖經曾為演出《舉重妖精金福珠》刻意把自己吃胖7kg，當時還胖到炸出雙下巴，引起網友熱議。<br />\n<br />\n昔日網友對於李聖經的印象總是嬌小身材，但事實上她是175公分高，一點也不嬌小！最近有網友搜出她過去為時尚品牌拍攝的照片，照片中她穿著細肩帶泳裝，露出白皙又細長的大長腿，嚇壞不少網友，該照片還在微博登上熱搜榜前三名。<br />\n<br />\n網友們不禁直呼：「這逆天的大長腿」、「實力羨慕」、「真的絕了」、「天使面孔魔鬼身材」、「能歌善舞，有才有貌有身材的全能女神 ​」、「我的媽？ ？ ？舉重妖精還以為姐姐是嬌小型的」、「大海啊全是水，聖經啊全是腿！」、「腿不僅是細關鍵是直」。<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h9pX1J3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh9pX1J3.jpg&h=4b2e4b94&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n這身材簡直就是一到靚麗的風景線啊，太完美了，最先映入眼簾的還是這雙腿吶！ ！​​​​<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dwL0Zww.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdwL0Zww.jpg&h=862a5f4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/enW0e4R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FenW0e4R.jpg&h=9a4cd1bc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"54f92436a059c8efc6f14131523211263d161df0","tid":1157132,"uid":123848,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T05:20:28.000Z","msg":"隻手成條枯枝咁啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20c587347d361a0ebe8c4b49a62bb7870ec690bf","tid":1157132,"uid":231132,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"54f92436a059c8efc6f14131523211263d161df0","tid":1157132,"uid":123848,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T05:20:28.000Z","msg":"隻手成條枯枝咁啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T05:23:17.000Z","msg":"(&macr;―&macr;٥) 有咩問題"},{"pid":"d4a6d035f2ff99ddfcbf3ba69cde70a8c437a4a7","tid":1157132,"uid":231132,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score